message.body: All juniors have class at 2:20 on monday :(
Aw damn.... =\ So that knocks out half you guys
Should I see if Sunny can go earlier? Or later?
I think she gets out of class at 6:10
We have openings after that!
Thanks
How's interview scheduling going?
Good! Waiting for Sunny to reply back cause I asked if she could do it later. Have not heard from Kayla or Ali. Everyone else is scheduled
Ok sounds good I'm really excited to meet all of them :)
Me too!! =)
My 2 credit theatre class got cancelled.....should I just give myself an easy semester?? Haha
Oh no :( umm depends on how it affects the rest of your schedule cause I know the double minor makes it tight
I'm gonna have to take 6 classes in one semester regardless.....haha. Guess Fall 2013 is gonna SUCK
Aw haha it'll be fine! Its been done before
Haha, it has been. Ugh, is it bad that I wanna go back to school?
I really do! This break has felt super long
It has!! Also, I filled out the 2 credits with a guitar class =)
Haha I'm so excited to do only 12 credits
Haha. You did it smart =P
Ugh no my gpa definitely suffered when I did 18 credits all the time
I'm hoping that beginning guitar will be an easy GPA boost, like my voice class was
Yeah I'm sure it will be
Do you find you prefer taking mostly speech classes? Like if I take 4 speech classes, am I going to go crazy? (Still trying to figure out my schedule....)
Well I think 4 speech classes alone is fine but that plus 2 other classes would be tough. Also I think taking 4 your sophomore year is too much
I am inclined to agree with you. Thank you! You're so wise
Hahaha you'll be fine don't worry. Remember I did a whole semester of no speech classes and ill still be fine
That's cause you're smart =P
Only sometimes haha
No ones switched out of bridges class :( lol
Oh noes! Haha
I feel bad!
Both classes are open, it's not the worst thing
.....I'm getting way too excited about being back in the city
Haha what are you looking forward to?
I don't know. Everything!! I'm getting dorm deco, haha
Aww cute haha my room literally has nothing I'm the least creative person ever
￼.....yeah, I'm a big deco person
Crazy lol
I'm freaking out. So the "group" project in artic is actually independent
And is worth 45% of our grade
..........oh my good heavens what? What do we do?
We slowly die next semester
Haha, touché. What does the project involve?
Some articulation and phonological analysis with three separate parts
Alright, so I'll miss you when we both die in that class
Haha we need to have a review of phonetics before it starts
Definitely! I'm happy that I'm taking phonetics next semester, haha
True it'll probably go hand in hand
Haha. I'm like....ready to go back to school, though
Its been forever
It feels like SO LONG
We still have a week and a half...
OHMYGOD STOP. Haha. I need to get back to a schedule
But once were back were gonna wish it was break again haha
Haha. It's how it always is, though. I just wanna chill with the EBoard and get things rolling
I know its been a long time!!
Just got crazy good pizza by West Broadway...I don't remember where or what it was, but it was delicious and we should go
Yesss so down
